## Attribution

If you use this project in your work, a citation or attribution would be appreciated:

### Citation Format

**APA Style:**
```
Singh, N. P. (2024). Machine Learning Algorithms - From Scratch & Scikit-Learn 
[Computer software]. GitHub. https://github.com/Nitin-Prata/Machine-learning-Algorithm
```

**BibTeX:**
```bibtex
@software{singh2024mlalgorithms,
  author = {Singh, Nitin Pratap},
  title = {Machine Learning Algorithms - From Scratch \& Scikit-Learn},
  year = {2024},
  publisher = {GitHub},
  url = {https://github.com/Nitin-Prata/Machine-learning-Algorithm}
}
```

**Chicago Style:**
```
Singh, Nitin Pratap. 2024. "Machine Learning Algorithms - From Scratch & Scikit-Learn." 
GitHub repository. https://github.com/Nitin-Prata/Machine-learning-Algorithm
```

