### Can I use this for commercial projects?
Yes! The MIT License allows commercial use.

### Do I need to include the license file?
Yes, you must include the LICENSE file with any distributions.

### Can I modify the code?
Absolutely! Feel free to modify and adapt the code for your needs.

### Do I need permission to use this?
No explicit permission needed. The MIT License grants you the rights automatically.

### Can I contribute back?
Contributions are always welcome! See CONTRIBUTING.md for guidelines.

### What if I find a bug?
Please open an issue on GitHub. While there's no warranty, we'll do our best to help!

